create .gitignore
create bare repo (xxx.git) on server (create folder, git --bare init .)
init local repo (git init)
add files here (git add .)
commit stuff here (git commit -m "Init message")
add remote repo to origins (i.e. git remote add origin ssh://aaaaa@bbb/path/to/cakephp/app.git)
push (git push origin master)
done!
(maybe clone repo on remote machine for usage (git clone xxx.git) )
